{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>TETHER BRAWL is an action-packed, top-down, 2-player game where co-operation is optional.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> JOIN THE DISCORD <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/DiscordCall-v002.png?t=1735216009\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcac Express your interest in receiving exclusive, free playtest access, catch up on updates and interact with the community.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FACE THE ROBOT ONSLAUGHT</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play various game modes, where players tackle relentless robot waves. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From varied arenas to character uniqueness and different enemies, every match is exciting.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stand united against the mechanical onslaught, or risk a crushing defeat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/FaceTheRobots.gif?t=1735216009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MASTER YOUR MOVES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every character, from Jeremiah's bat-swinging might to Beccia's sharp throwing, demands skill. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perfectly timing your skills and mastering abilities is essential.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead the charge and dominate the arena with calculated moves.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595020/extras/MasterYourMoves.gif?t=1735216009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TRUST IS OPTIONAL</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">CO-OP and WAVES m